<p><img src="/media/13087233/adobestock_138931146-1.jpeg" alt="Summer 2022 RHS offer" /></p>
<p><strong>We are excited to partner with RHS and offer you £100 off your <a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays">summer 2022 holiday</a>.</strong></p>
<p><span>If you have never travelled with Inghams before, here’s a little bit about us…</span></p>
<p><span>We’ve been helping people explore their passions and interests for over 85 years. We take you to the places we know best across Europe. All holidays are flexible and tailored, with a choice of flight times, local airports, durations, multi-centre stays, tours, accommodation and activities.</span></p>
<p><span>So, whether you're hoping to enjoy some fresh mountain air in <a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Austria</a>, fill up on the best food in <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a>, or soak up the scenery in <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> - you can experience more with Inghams.</span></p>
<p><span>And you can rest assured that we've put <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/about-us/in-safe-hands">extra measures</a> in place to keep you and your money safe. You can enjoy total peace of mind when you book your summer holiday with Inghams. </span></p>
